This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with automated digital histopathology image segmentation. Additionally, the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) suggests that it may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of information retrieval techniques, which could place it in the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Finally, the mention of whole-slide images (WSI) viewers suggests that it may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
